    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable daily driver for someone willing to put in a little work. The exterior shows some visible fading on the hood and roof, along with several scuffs and door dings from city parking. Inside, the upholstery has noticeable wear on the driver's seat and a few stains on the carpet. Mechanically, it runs and drives, though it will likely need new brake pads and a suspension tune-up soon. It's an honest car at an honest price for those looking for value over perfection.",
